deps2dot
========

Usage
=====

::

    deps2dot [--help|-h] [--version]

Where::

    --help|-h           Show this help message and exit.
    --version           Show version number and exit.

Description
===========

Dependencies
============

Tested on OSX. Should work elsewhere.
Tested on Python 3.2.
Doesn't strictly depend upon, but uses the output of, snakefood.

Install
=======

::

    pip install deps2dot

Known Problems
==============

Alternatives
============

Snakefood contains an executable 'sfood-graph' that performs the same
transformation, but with different stylistic choices regarding the
